title: 2010 Thai FA Cup
text:
The <a href="Thai%20FA%20Cup">Thai FA Cup</a> 2010 () is the 15th season of <a href="Thailand">Thailand</a> knockout <a href="Association%20football">football</a> competition. The tournament is organized by the <a href="Football%20Association%20of%20Thailand">Football Association of Thailand</a>.
The cup winner were guaranteed a place in the <a href="2011%20AFC%20Cup">2011 AFC Cup</a>.
